videos.description: Jordan McCabe aggressively snatches the ball away and Sean McNeil finishes off the defensive transition with a smooth layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (WVU capitalizes off steal with McNeil's layup) 2020/12/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: WVU capitalizes off steal with McNeil's layup

videos.description: Taz Sherman steals the pass and tosses an alley-oop to Oscar Tshiebwe.  On the next Richmond possession, Miles McBride intercepts the pass and throws down the one-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (WVU scores off back-to-back steals) 2020/12/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: WVU scores off back-to-back steals

videos.description: Tyler Burton tries to drive in for the dunk, but Derek Culver is there for the block with authority.
